Toya: After coming to this neighborhood, I found a partner, met new friends and was introduced to a new genre of music.
Toya: The time we've spent together has allowed me to accept myself for who I am. I was able to come to terms with my past and bring it into the present.
Toya: I wouldn't have been able to overcome the obstacles that I faced along the way without all of you. I was able to keep moving forward as a result.
Toya: I was able to make it this far.
Toya: I want to see the impact the song I wrote has on this neighborhood. I want to see how far I can go.
Toya: Which is why I'm going to give this day absolutely everything I have.
